 <i>a two-all draw</i>

00:04:51.159 --> 00:04:52.392 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>on the scoreboard.</i>

00:04:52.425 --> 00:04:55.462 position:19% line:83% align:start
-You're the best! Yeah!
-You're the best! Yeah!

00:04:55.495 --> 00:04:57.565 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Mamoru]
Tsubasa, Taro!

00:04:57.598 --> 00:04:59.499 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[laughs]
-Yeah! We tied.

00:04:59.534 --> 00:05:00.868 position:27% line:83% align:start
-You guys did it!
-That was great, man!

00:05:00.902 --> 00:05:03.638 position:16% line:83% align:start
-You two are a great duo!
