[female fan]
What a great match, kids!

00:18:43.256 --> 00:18:45.026 position:19% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>The crowd cheers</i>
 <i>and applauds</i>

00:18:45.059 --> 00:18:46.293 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>for both teams.</i>

00:18:46.326 --> 00:18:48.362 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>They played like</i>
 <i>professionals!</i>

00:18:48.395 --> 00:18:51.866 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>It was a great match,</i>
 <i>a real battle of titans.</i>

00:18:55.737 --> 00:18:57.705 position:19% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>Team Nankatsu's</i>
 <i>locker room...</i>

00:18:58.906 --> 00:19:00.541 position:24% line:83% align:start
Why the long face,
everybody?

00:19:00.575 --> 00:19:01.274 position:30% line:89% align:start
Don't sweat it.

00:19:01.308 --> 00:19:02.710 position:27% line:83% align:start
It doesn't matter
if we lost.

00:19:02.744 --> 00:19:04.411 position:21% line:89% align:start
You played your best.

00:19:04.444 --> 00:19:06.380 position:19% line:83% align:start
Not everything's lost.
Relax, guys.

00:19:06.413 --> 00:19:08.181 position:35% line:83% align:start
This match
doesn't determine

00:19:08.215 --> 00:19:10.317 position:30% line:83% align:start
if we're out of
the national tournament.

00:19:10.350 --> 00:19:12.486 position:47% line:83% align:start
Oh!
Yeah, that's true.

00:19:12.520 --> 00:19:14.555 position:30% line:83% align:start
Because in the
elimination phase,

00:19:14.589 --> 00:19:17.424 position:16% line:83% align:start
two teams from each group
can make it out.

00:19:17.457 --> 00:19:19.393 position:24% line:83% align:start
If we win the next
four matches that follow,

00:19:19.426 --> 00:19:21.596 position:24% line:83% align:start
we will still be in
the national tournament.

00:19:21.629 --> 00:19:22.730 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you're right

00:19:22.764 --> 00:19:24.666 position:21% line:89% align:start
We can still do this.

00:19:24.699 --> 00:19:25.733 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:19:25.767 --> 00:19:26.634 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're the captain.

00:19:26.668 --> 00:19:29.302 position:27% line:83% align:start
You can't put all
the blame on yourself.

00:19:29.336 --> 00:19:30.905 position:27% line:83% align:start
Leave this defeat
in the past.

00:19:30.938 --> 00:19:34.042 position:13% line:83% align:start
What's important now is to
win all the next matches.

00:19:34.075 --> 00:19:35.375 position:19% line:89% align:start
If we win our matches,

00:19:35.409 --> 00:19:39.547 position:19% line:83% align:start
we can go head-to-head
with Meiwa again later on.

00:19:39.580 --> 00:19:40.480 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:19:41.381 --> 00:19:43.450 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's it, Captain.
We can still win.

00:19:43.483 --> 00:19:45.586 position:19% line:83% align:start
Don't get discouraged.
You got that?

00:19:45.620 --> 00:19:48.221 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chatter]

00:19:48.255 --> 00:19:49.624 position:27% line:89% align:start
Tadashi speaking.

00:19:50.091 --> 00:19:51.458 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:19:51.491 --> 00:19:53.528 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Shiroyama] Hey, Yuzo,
this is for you.

00:19:53.561 --> 00:19:54.562 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:19:55.462 --> 00:19:56.597 position:21% line:89% align:start
Yeah, buddy, we lost.

00:19:56.631 --> 00:19:58.900 position:35% line:83% align:start
But it was
an incredible match.

00:19:58.933 --> 00:20:00.267 position:27% line:83% align:start
You really outdid
yourself, Yuzo.

00:20:00.300 --> 00:20:01.569 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'm proud of you.

00:20:01.602 --> 00:20:03.203 position:27% line:83% align:start
Thank you so much
for that, Genzo.

00:20:03.236 --> 00:20:04.138 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:20:04.172 --> 00:20:05.405 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
 <i>I'm asking you...</i>

00:20:05.439 --> 00:20:07.141 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Take care of our goal</i>
 <i>until I can come back.</i>

00:20:07.175 --> 00:20:09.209 position:44% line:83% align:start
Yeah!
Don't you worry about it.

00:20:09.242 --> 00:20:10.277 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
 <i>It's a deal then.</i>

00:20:10.310 --> 00:20:12.080 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>Can you put</i>
 <i>Tsubasa on, please?</i>

00:20:12.113 --> 00:20:15.315 position:10% line:83% align:start
Uh... Yeah, I'll put him on.
Just wait.

00:20:15.348 --> 00:20:17.618 position:41% line:83% align:start
Hello?
Do you hear me?

00:20:17.652 --> 00:20:18.653 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah...

00:20:19.620 --> 00:20:20.621 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:20:21.022 --> 00:20:21.889 position:35% line:89% align:start
Of course.

00:20:22.456 --> 00:20:23.725 position:24% line:89% align:start
Leave it all to me.

00:20:23.758 --> 00:20:26.326 position:21% line:83% align:start
All we have to do is
win the next four matches,

00:20:26.359 --> 00:20:27.995 position:24% line:83% align:start
and we can qualify
for the finals

00:20:28.029 --> 00:20:29.296 position:24% line:83% align:start
-of the tournament.
-[laughing]

00:20:29.329 --> 00:20:31.498 position:13% line:83% align:start
Don't you worry. We'll take
care of it, Genzo.

00:20:31.532 --> 00:20:32.265 position:38% line:89% align:start
No sweat.

00:20:32.299 --> 00:20:33.968 position:10% line:89% align:start
Exactly, we're going to win.

00:20:34.001 --> 00:20:35.837 position:13% line:89% align:start
Isn't that right, everyone?

00:20:35.870 --> 00:20:37.138 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:20:37.171 --> 00:20:38.305 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:20:38.338 --> 00:20:40.307 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Genzo] <i>I'm counting on</i>
 <i>all of you guys.</i>

00:20:40.340 --> 00:20:42.442 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll try to recover</i>
 <i>as fast as possible</i>

00:20:42.476 --> 00:20:43.711 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>so I can play</i>
 <i>with you all.</i>

00:20:43.745 --> 00:20:45.646 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>We'll win the national</i>
 <i>tournament together.</i>

00:20:49.416 --> 00:20:51.351 position:16% line:83% align:start
[narr] <i>In the first round</i>
 <i>of the tournament,</i>

00:20:51.384 --> 00:20:54.055 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Furano got</i>
 <i>a win over Team Nagano</i>

00:20:54.088 --> 00:20:56.124 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>in their first encounter,</i>
 <i>2 to 1.</i>

00:20:56.157 --> 00:20:57.357 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nagano couldn't</i>
 <i>keep up with</i>

00:20:57.390 --> 00:20:59.227 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>the teamwork of Furano.</i>

00:20:59.259 --> 00:21:01.394 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>And on the other side,</i>
 <i>in the fourth group,</i>

00:21:01.428 --> 00:21:03.731 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Musashi goes up</i>
 <i>against Team Jonan.</i>

00:21:03.765 --> 00:21:05.465 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And here is</i>
 <i>Prince Jun Misugi</i>

00:21:05.499 --> 00:21:06.801 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>intercepting the ball.</i>

00:21:06.834 --> 00:21:09.302 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:21:09.336 --> 00:21:11.072 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, I'm so jealous!

00:21:11.105 --> 00:21:12.707 position:16% line:89% align:start
All the ladies love him.

00:21:12.740 --> 00:21:13.741 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:21:14.575 --> 00:21:17.178 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>What an elegant feint.</i>

00:21:17.211 --> 00:21:18.513 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>And a beautiful jump.</i>

00:21:19.680 --> 00:21:22.282 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Jun Misugi plays as if</i>
 <i>he were painting a canvas</i>

00:21:22.315 --> 00:21:24.384 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and all of the crowd</i>
 <i>watches the maestro.</i>

00:21:24.417 --> 00:21:26.721 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Jun] <i>Tsubasa, I'm really</i>
 <i>looking forward</i>

00:21:26.754 --> 00:21:29.322 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>to get on the pitch</i>
 <i>to face you.</i>

00:21:29.356 --> 00:21:30.625 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>Jun Misugi.</i>

00:21:32.026 --> 00:21:32.727 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:21:33.227 --> 00:21:34.294 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Goal!</i>

00:21:34.327 --> 00:21:36.463 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Musashi has</i>
 <i>an overwhelming lead</i>

00:21:36.496 --> 00:21:38.166 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>in the beginning</i>
 <i>of the match.</i>

00:21:38.199 --> 00:21:39.834 position:35% line:83% align:start
That's how
it's done, Captain!

00:21:44.337 --> 00:21:47.575 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>First, it was Kojiro,</i>
 <i>and now it's Jun.</i>

00:21:47.608 --> 00:21:50.711 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'm sure he'll be</i>
 <i>an amazing opponent.</i>

00:21:50.745 --> 00:21:52.312 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Jun Misugi.</i>

00:21:52.345 --> 00:21:55.149 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>If we want to win</i>
 <i>the national tournament,</i>

00:21:55.183 --> 00:21:56.951 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>we'll have to</i>
 <i>defeat him first.</i>

00:22:01.488 --> 00:22:04.457 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Kojiro] <i>I thought I had</i>
 <i>everything under control.</i>

00:22:04.491 --> 00:22:06.093 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>My shot was</i>
 <i>unstoppable.</i>

00:22:09.496 --> 00:22:11.165 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Someway somehow,</i>

00:22:11.199 --> 00:22:12.800 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>he managed to divert it.</i>

00:22:12.834 --> 00:22:15.903 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>He prevented the ball</i>
 <i>from going into the goal.</i>

00:22:15.937 --> 00:22:17.404 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>The worst part is that...</i>

00:22:19.472 --> 00:22:21.876 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I lost the last battle</i>
 <i>against him.</i>

00:22:23.144 --> 00:22:24.545 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Kaori]
Are you Kojiro Hyuga?

00:22:24.579 --> 00:22:25.345 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:22:26.346 --> 00:22:29.317 position:19% line:83% align:start
We've taken an interest
in you, young man.

00:22:29.349 --> 00:22:31.252 position:33% line:83% align:start
Are you guys,
player scouts?

00:22:31.285 --> 00:22:32.053 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes.

00:22:33.087 --> 00:22:35.623 position:30% line:83% align:start
We represent...
the Toho Academy.

